North Sentinel Island has been untouched by modern civilisation for 60,000 years . 
  The islanders are hostile to outsiders and have rejected contact with the outside world . 
  The Indian government has established a three-mile exclusion zone to protect the islanders . 
  North Sentinel Island is located in the Bay of Bengal and is about the size of Manhattan . 
  Members of the Sentinelese tribe have been known to fire arrows at helicopters . 
 